#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.nanargmax.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.nanargmax"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanargmax.nanargmax:1 of
msgid ""
"Return the indices of the maximum values in the specified axis ignoring "
"NaNs. For all-NaN slices ``ValueError`` is raised. Warning: the results "
"cannot be trusted if a slice contains only NaNs and -Infs."
msgstr ""
"返回指定轴上忽略 NaN 的最大值的索引。对于全为 NaN 的切片会引发 ``"
"ValueError``。警告：如果切片只包含 NaN 和 -Inf，则结果不可信。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanargmax.nanargmax of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanargmax.nanargmax:6 of
msgid "Input data."
msgstr "输入数据。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanargmax.nanargmax:8 of
msgid "Axis along which to operate.  By default flattened input is used."
msgstr "运算的轴。默认使用展平后的输入。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanargmax.nanargmax:10 of
msgid ""
"Alternate output tensor in which to place the result.  The default is "
"``None``; if provided, it must have the same shape as the expected "
"output, but the type will be cast if necessary. See `doc.ufuncs` for "
"details."
msgstr ""
"用于存放结果的替代输出张量。默认为 ``None``；如果提供，它必须与期望输出"
"具有相同的形状，但类型会在必要时进行转换。详见 `doc.ufuncs`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanargmax.nanargmax of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanargmax.nanargmax:16 of
msgid "**index_array** -- An tensor of indices or a single index value."
msgstr "**index_array** -- 一个索引张量或单个索引值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanargmax.nanargmax of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanargmax.nanargmax:19 of
msgid ":py:obj:`argmax`, :py:obj:`nanargmin`"
msgstr ""

